author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-CTW Investment Urges Tesla Shareholders To Vote Against Re-Election Of Directors Antonio Gracias, Kimball Musk, And James Murdoch
text:
May 9 (Reuters) - Tesla Inc:
* CTW INVESTMENT GROUP URGES TESLA INC SHAREHOLDERS TO VOTE AGAINST RE-ELECTION OF DIRECTORS ANTONIO GRACIAS, KIMBALL MUSK, AND JAMES R. MURDOCH Source text: ( bit.ly/2I8cgcH ) Further company coverage: (Reuters.Briefs@thomsonreuters.com)
